      • writeMRMCFile

        public void writeMRMCFile(double[][] t00,
                 double[][] t01,
                 double[][] t10,
                 double[][] t11,
                 double[] auc,
                 java.lang.String filename,
                 int fileNum)
        Writes the results of a simulation experiment as ROC scores to a text file, formatted to be read by iMRMC or equivalent software
        Parameters:
        t00 - Matrix for normal cases, modality 0
        t01 - Matrix for normal cases, modality 1
        t10 - Matrix for disease cases, modality 0
        t11 - Matrix for disease cases, modality 1
        auc - AUCs of experiment1
        filename - Filename prefix (is a timestamp) for a particular batch of output files
        fileNum - The number of this particular experiment in the batch
